Overview

Restore Windows and recover lost data instantly 

FarStone RestoreIT is an innovative real time data & system protection solution. 
RestoreIT automatically creates snapshots before changes are made to your system. 
RestoreIT simply returns your PC to a time when it was working properly and your data was intact. 
In the event of data loss or system crash, RestoreIT can revert a system to a normal state in seconds. 
The result is all issues will be fixed no matter what went wrong. 
Lost data recovered and unstable system restored immediately
